Dockerfile and ascripts for building the x86_64 version of the official Unity
Webrtc plugin.

Requires approximately 40gig disk space.

# To install docker into a fresh environment (ubuntu) run the following
bash bash install-docker.sh

# To build the docker image.
sudo ./build.sh

# To execute the script using the image.
sudo ./run.sh

The final webrtc-android.zip artifact built in the container will be available
in the "result" folder.
